window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>My husband. My villain.</b> </p> <p>We started with death and blood. </p> <p>We started with games and carnal pleasure. </p> <p>Adrian and I shouldn’t have been together. </p> <p>He’s wrong. </p> <p>I’m wrong. </p> <p>What we have is the epitome of disaster. </p> <p>Yet, it’s impossible to stop.</p> <p>My husband will either destroy me or I’ll destroy him.</p> <p><i>This book is part of a trilogy and is not standalone.</i></p>"; 
